Premier Inn for Fulham
Posted on 29th April 2016 by lookwestlondon
Fulham is to get a hub Premier Inn, as Whitbread ramps up the roll out of the brand across London.
TheLillie Road site will be the 13th hub by Premier Inn. It will be a new 83-bedroomhotel for what Whitbread descibes as astrong, established catchment that is set to improve dramatically.
A planning application is expected in summer 2016.
